org.apache.jena.propertytable

Interface PropertyTable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PropertyTableArrayImpl, PropertyTableHashMapImpl

    public interface PropertyTable
    PropertyTable is designed to be a table of RDF terms, or Nodes in Jena. Each Column of the PropertyTable has an unique columnKey Node of the predicate (or p for short). Each Row of the PropertyTable has an unique rowKey Node of the subject (or s for short). You can use getColumn() to get the Column by its columnKey Node of the predicate, while getRow() for Row.
